 1970er Jahren suchten Designer hingegen nach neuen Küchenkonzepten.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aART / History / General.2bisacsh  aEinbauküche, Frankfurter Küche, Margarete Schütte-Lihotzky.1 aBarta, Ilsebill, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHaslinger, Ingrid, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKönig, Julia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMuttenthaler, Roswitha, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOttillinger, Eva B., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOttillinger, Eva B., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2015z9783110438642oZDB-23-DKA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.7767/978320579385440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783205793854423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783205793854.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DKAb2015